dcterms:description: The Shenzhen dataset contains taxi track data, road network data, weather data, and POI data from Luohu District, Shenzhen, collected from January 1 to January 31, 2015. The study area includes 156 road sections and nine types of POIs: food services, enterprises, shopping services, transportation services, education living services, medical services, accommodation services, and others. Weather data includes temperature, weather conditions, wind speed, humidity, barometric pressure, and visibility at 15-minute intervals.
dcterms:title: Shenzhen Dataset
